column5: With some good sales, I was able to up grade. Rotary peak vise. Got a great deal on it. Floor model. Last one left.
Will pay for itself in no time with dem bugs
Very nice vise it will make your tying easier I bet. Art
Already paid for Scott. Sure will Art. No more taking the hook out to turn upside down and can wind materials much more precise. I hope.LOL
The Easter bunny came early nice
